com.atc.simulator.flightdata.system_state_database

Class SystemStateDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atc.simulator.flightdata.system_state_database.SystemStateDatabase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PredictionEngineSystemStateDatabase

    public class SystemStateDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a very simple placeholder SystemStateDatabase, which just keeps track of all items it receives, and notifies its listeners whenever it receives an update. In the future it will probably want its own thread to cull items which have been sitting in the database for too long without getting used. (e.g. aircraft that have moved to other sectors)
